<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Decision 6) : Heartbeat</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Disconnect the ink tube from printheads 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> (See<xref class="- topic/xref " keyref="02ADJU004" href="GUID-0A9015C3-DC1C-417D-8B80-D6AE9F8C4B83.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 The (expired) ink replacement procedure including flushing tubes?>02 The ink replacement procedure</xref> , Chapter 3. Refill the system with new ink : Step 7 - 27 (end)) 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Is there a heartbeat after this procedure ? 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Decision 7) : Electrical issue</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Check/ re-seat the electrical wiring and connectors of the ink pump(s). 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Action 7): Solve electrical issue 
